                <note rend="inline" type="source">No. 18.</note>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Fish</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Hoffman</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic"> Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1870-07-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 16, 1870.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Protection of North Germans in French territory by American representative can
                    only be given at request of North Germany, and with assent of France. Examine
                    request of Mr. Moustier of July 19, ‘67, to United States to protect French in
                    Mexico.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
